sys_openapi.description:
The data API provides access to any database for which it is enabled. The API represents databases, views, view entries, and documents in JSON format.
**Important**: This version of the OpenAPI spec (**data.yaml**) includes data API changes from the XPages Extension Library release 9.0.1.v09_02. This includes new operations on attachments, agents and forms. If you are using a version before 9.0.1.v09_02, consider using an earlier version of the spec.
sys_openapi.name: IBM Domino Data API
